{"metadata":{"title":"OUDSCheckbox","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"15.0","name":"macOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"16.0","name":"tvOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"11.0","name":"watchOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Suggestions"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeBusinessTools"}],"ty